18:20.428 --> 18:21.429
oh.

18:26.934 --> 18:28.770
(peggy)
oh, ooh!

18:28.770 --> 18:30.221
[snorting]

18:30.221 --> 18:31.806
what the hey?

18:31.806 --> 18:34.275
It's a little pig
in the house.

18:34.275 --> 18:37.195
Oh, this is crazy.
It's fun like in that movie.

18:37.195 --> 18:40.198
.
Let's chase it together.
I'll grab it
and you snatch the bow

18:40.698 --> 18:42.617
it'll be romantic.

18:42.617 --> 18:45.036
Come on, it's pig-chasing.

18:45.036 --> 18:48.456
(bobby)
mom, dad,
there's a pig in the house.

18:48.456 --> 18:51.576
Oh, peggy, I'm tryin'
to be romantic here.

18:51.576 --> 18:54.212
.
I just wanted
to make things right again

18:54.212 --> 18:56.331
for that, you would
need a time machine.

18:56.331 --> 18:58.416
And all you have is a pig.

18:58.916 --> 19:01.836
You can't just make up
a romantic story for us.

19:01.836 --> 19:04.005
The great ones
just happen naturally.

19:04.005 --> 19:05.673
And right now,

19:05.673 --> 19:08.176
neither of us knows
if one will
ever happen again.

19:08.559 --> 19:09.560
But, peggy...

19:09.844 --> 19:11.979
[pig squealing]
ah, ah! Ugh!

19:11.979 --> 19:14.232
[growling]

19:14.232 --> 19:15.733
my back.

19:15.733 --> 19:17.735
Congratulations, hank.

19:17.735 --> 19:20.104
You just ruined
one of my favorite movies.

19:22.240 --> 19:23.741
When's your date
going to get here?

19:24.242 --> 19:25.243
How should I know?

19:25.243 --> 19:27.245
I don't even know
for sure who she is,

19:27.662 --> 19:29.580
or if her leg is fully healed.

19:29.580 --> 19:30.581
Where should we hide?

19:30.581 --> 19:32.033
(bobby)
in the closet.

19:32.533 --> 19:35.036
And don't play wit
h the dry-cleaning bag,
you could suffocate.

19:35.036 --> 19:37.789
.
Hey, where's connie?
She'd want to see this

19:37.789 --> 19:39.540
I thought she'd be here.

19:39.540 --> 19:43.044
(luanne)
bobby, your secret
admirer is here.

19:46.380 --> 19:47.381
Grandma?

19:47.848 --> 19:49.683
Happy valentine's day,
boo-boo!

19:49.683 --> 19:51.469
no!

19:52.470 --> 19:53.354
[chuckling]

19:53.354 --> 19:55.356
.
your grandmother loves you

19:56.057 --> 19:57.858
[boggle cubes rattling]

19:57.858 --> 19:59.860
you cannot believe
what hank has put me through.

20:00.361 --> 20:02.363
I--I have never seen
a more pathetic series

20:02.363 --> 20:04.648
of unromantic,
childish stunts.

20:04.949 --> 20:05.950
Oh, shug.

20:06.450 --> 20:09.737
First, he thinks flowers
are going to make
everything better.

20:09.737 --> 20:11.238
.
They just don't get it

