21:23.360 --> 21:26.864
Well, I thought about it
and decided to make you

21:26.864 --> 21:28.782
beef wellington.

21:28.782 --> 21:30.618
Beef wellington, huh?

21:30.618 --> 21:32.403
How'd it turn out this time?

21:32.403 --> 21:35.739
Well, I'd have to say
it's pretty perfect.

21:35.739 --> 21:37.658
Of course it is,
that's your specialty.

21:38.159 --> 21:39.160
That's right.

21:39.160 --> 21:41.662
And I baked you a cherry pie

21:42.163 --> 21:44.465
with a golden-brown crust.

21:44.465 --> 21:47.168
Boy! I tell you what, peggy.
That's my favorite.

21:47.168 --> 21:48.335
Mmm-hmm.

22:01.482 --> 22:02.983
[dish shatters]

22:02.983 --> 22:04.485
(peggy)
mother, be careful.

22:04.985 --> 22:07.938
That woman in that movie
was 30 years younger than you.

22:10.441 --> 22:11.609
[pig squeals]

22:11.609 --> 22:14.111
(luanne)
stay outta here!
This is my room, you pig!

22:15.412 --> 22:19.166
A pig in the house
. It's crazy. It's fun.

22:19.166 --> 22:21.335
Come on, bobby
.

